Subject: Re: [T2] Carb Mixture

Seat the screw in until it is gently seated, i.e., won't turn in anymore. Do
this GENTLY so you don't damage the seat or needle tip. Once it's fully
seated, back it back out  2 full turns, then another 1/2 turn (180 degrees).
Done!
Courtney

 
